headline: Match Group (MTCH): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Match Group’s shares (currently trading at $31.64) have posted a disappointing 14% loss while the S&P 500 was down 1.4%. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
